      "body": "**Run 0003 T2 reconcile: assigned session did nothing, but a large uncommitted picrep+FBC pile is stranded and a stale Horizon process is still alive.** (Session `0022-ground`.)\n\n**1. The T2 session failed on a bad resume.** `0020-horizon-T2` started with the \"Continue your previous task\" prompt but its engine reported `No conversation found with session ID` and exited in ~1s (0 tokens, returncode 1). Same failure family as `I-0072` \u2014 the harness tried to resume a conversation that no longer exists. Nothing to reconcile from it.\n\n**2. A stranded Horizon process is still running.** `claude -p ... --model claude-fable-5` (PID `47819`, ~37 min elapsed) is alive but **idle**: no `lake`/`lean` child, no file edits in 33 min, only its own `lean-lsp-mcp`. It appears hung rather than working. It nominally owns the AJC working tree, which is why I did **not** commit or build. **Please decide whether to kill it.**\n\n**3. A ~999-LOC uncommitted pile is stranded in the AJC tree** (nothing committed since the T8 rescue `eed5383`). It is genuine progress but **incomplete and unverified**:\n- **picrep rewire (great news):** `picSharp` is now the real relative functor `PicSharp.relPresheaf`, gated on a new `HasRationalSection` hypothesis \u2014 the sanctioned fix from `I-0060` that removes the opaque `Classical.choice \u27e8sorry\u27e9` and correctly avoids the absolute-vs-relative FALSE-axiom trap. `FGAPicRepresentability.lean` + `RelPicFunctor.lean` current sources have fresh oleans (compiled). Universe bumped to `Type (u+1)`.\n- **FBC/T2:** new `AffinePushPullEssImage.lean` (~430 LOC) never built; `CechHigherDirectImageUnconditional.lean` current source is stale (never compiled). `IdentityComponent.lean` + root module also stale/unbuilt.\n- Net effect: **no green full build exists** for this pile. Committing now would freeze a broken mid-rewire intermediate, so I left it in place.\n\n**4. Git identity is now configured** on all ledgers (the `I-0072` fix step-1 was applied), so `horizon commit` should work once the work is finished and verified.\n\n**Recommended human action:** kill the stale PID `47819` if confirmed hung, then relaunch a clean T2/picrep session to finish and verify the pile (full `lake build`) before committing. See `recommendation.md`.",
